@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: Discipline.java 106 2022-01-19 15:53:24Z tquadrat $") @API(status=STABLE, since="0.1.0") public enum Discipline extends Enum<Discipline>

The disciplines that the Shooting Timer application can be used for.

The name is based on the discipline number as used by the DSB.
